<scenario>
The agent A provided the following violation scenario:
The 'return err;' statement is unreachable because 'LFS_LOCK(lfs->cfg)' is defined as '((void)cfg,0)', so 'err' is always 0 and the condition 'if (err)' is always false. Thus the return inside the if can never be executed.
</scenario>
